modName: Vampire cuirass with chains for CHSBHC
summary: Vampire cuirass with chains for CHSBHC
descriptionHtml:
This adds CHSBHC BBP support to the Vampire cuirass with chains for UNPBBBP and DreamGirl body by newmiller 
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/46696//?

       [IMG]http://i39.tinypic.com/e0gxeu.jpg[/IMG]

=======Description================
This is a conversion of newmiller Vampire cuirass with chains converted to fit CHSBHC body. The armor Craftable in leather - names begins from 'Vampire cuirass, Mod has 4 color variants of cuirass. Supports weight slider.

Recommended:
========================
Skyrim 1.9.32+ and SKSE 1.6.13+ is required.
(Option) SKYUI 3.4+ is required.
CHSBHC body mod and BBP -Breast and Butt Physics 
FNIS Behavior Files and Generator 4.0.2
CBBE-CHSBHC-UNP-ADEC-Human Argonian Khajiit Texture-4096
NoMaaM Breathing Idles BBB 
NoMaaM Walk BBB - inverse orientation
